Preconditions:
- The input string `text` is not null.
- The input string `text` contains at least one word.

Postconditions:
- The returned string has an equal number of spaces between every pair of adjacent words.
- The number of spaces between every pair of adjacent words is maximized.
- If there are extra spaces after redistributing them equally, they are placed at the end of the string.
- The length of the returned string is the same as the length of the input string `text`.